Introduction:
Searching for Swedish to English dictionary or English to Swedish which works without internet (offline) ? This Swedish - English free dictionary app is perfect for your need.
This dictionary app contains large database of words which provide unique experience to you. This is offline dictionary. you need not to worry about the internet connection availability.
It works smoothly without internet connection. Install this dictionary online. it has beautiful user interface which provide great user experience. Everything in this App is well organized.
It has a unique design. This is best dictionary from Swedish to English. While searching the meanings of words from Swedish to English or English - Swedish, this great app provide
many tools to fit your needs. This is available for free download.

The Dictionary words with meanings are best for student or for any other person
who is interested in languages. In this word meaning app, you can get word diction or can know how to define words. This Swedish - English software is free. This app is easy to use.
While comparing different dictionaries, i.e. Online dictionary and offline dictionary, the offline one is best choice. it is fast and portable. it is better than online dictionary download.
This app also falls in this category. it is portable app. you can carry it in your smart phone in your pocket. you can study words whenever you needed at any place. All the words meanings are at your
single tap. you can get reference of words from multiple languages. This Swedish English is ok to download for offline needs. It includes a-z (a to z) words of both Swedish and English.
it also contains pronunciation of words. This best free Swedish dictionary will provide you unique experience.

you can find word meaning and can translate meaning as well in this meaning app. This Bilingual dictionary is best mobile dictionary. This phone dictionary is pocket dictionary. so it is portable.
this is short, concise and fast to translate words meanings. you can find word that can be used as noun, pronoun, verb, adverb, adjective, prefix, suffix, conjunction, interjection, abbreviation, phrase, preposition etc.
this apps works without internet connection. it helps you to convert Swedish to English or English to Swedish. it works as word translator which is offline.



How to Use:
After starting the app, you will be presented a screen containing an area to enter words. To translate Swedish to English, enter the word of Swedish, it will show translation in English.
To translate English to Swedish, enter the word of English, it will show the translation in Swedish. so, is not it very simple? There is also search history which you can access from main menu.
It includes the words that you have searched previously. All words are arranged in a list. you can again search them by simply taping them.

There is also a bookmark fearure. if you searched a word and want to save it for future study, just simple tap the 'add to bookmarked' button. It will add the word to your bookmark list.
The book mark list can be accessed from main menu. it lists all the bookmarked words. You can tap on a word to search it again.



Feature:
★ 100,000+ words
★ Beautiful User Interface
★ User Friendly
★ Bilingual Dictionary
★ Completely Offline Dictionary
★ Save Search History
★ You can Bookmark words



Note:
Sometimes, fonts are not installed on your phone. So, words are not properly displayed. Phone manufacturer are responsible for this. There is no problem in app. You should install the respective fonts that are not displayed properly.
